            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "I see, that's unfortunate. To clarify what I'm trying to use it for, I just learned about `--listen` and tried to add neovim support to https://github.com/AndrewRadev/vimrunner. It's not a particular priority to me, so I'm happy to just follow this issue and give it a go when it's available.\r\n\r\nIt would also be convenient to export it as `--serverlist`, similar to what Vim provides, though I can work around its lack.",
